---
title: Venison, Beef & Cherry Tomato Bolognese with Spaghetti & Parmesan
description: Packed with the rich flavours of a classic Italian tomato sauce, you'll find it hard to believe this venison and beef bolognese didn't involve hours of cooking. Plus, with thin strips of leek hidden in the sauce, it creates a beautifully textured and mouth-watering meal everyone will love.
